msgid "Expedition to R'lyeh"
msgstr "拉莱耶探险"

msgid "Interlude II: Expedition to R'lyeh"
msgstr "幕间故事II：拉莱耶探险"

msgid ""
"It is early evening when you first see the ancient city. You emerge from your cabin to see Andy and Ruby staring out at a jagged, bleak skyline off the starboard bow. The ancient city is a tangle of collapsed towers, labyrinthine boroughs, and jagged paths that loop in on themselves like a rat’s nest. Andy nearly drops his camera as a choppy wave lifts and then drops the nose of the ship with a sharp crash."
"“You’re seeing this. It’s real. Tell me it’s real,” Andy says, furiously loading more film into his scuffed camera. You and the rest of the crew marvel at the mind-bending skyline with a mixture of awe and dread. Seawater pours from the mouths of alien effigies and ancient sepulchres. Strange ephemeral shapes flit in and out of the obsidian canyons of R’lyeh. It is unlike anything built by human hands."
"You catch yourself saying the city’s name under your breath. Even the unflappable Ruby seems dumbstruck as the ship sails past a ring of rocky shoals into a broad cove. After making landfall, the expedition camps on the black-sanded beach, at the foot of a towering obsidian spire. Menacing, gargantuan doors set in the tower’s base loom like silent sentinels. There is hardly a word between the expedition members on the first night; Andy spends the evening poring over an obsidian stone set with glowing glyphs, while Ruby lovingly reorganizes her tool bag."
"In the morning, you discuss which route to take. Tillinghast has provided enough diving equipment, climbing gear, and rations to explore inland for at least two weeks before you would need to return to the beach. Andy and Ruby are at odds, however. Andy wants to follow the coastline to the ruined western wall near the mouth of the cove. Ruby, perennially comfortable with heights, wants to take to the skyline to map the city. She points excitedly at a distant, cathedral-like structure further inland."
msgstr ""
"你第一次看见这座古老城市已是傍晚时分。你从船舱里走了出来，发现安迪和露比凝视着右舷方向崎岖荒凉的天际线。古城一片狼藉，倒塌的塔楼，迷宫一样的市区，蜿蜒的道路环环相扣，看上去就像老鼠窝。一阵猛浪升起，又狠狠地落在船头，惊得安迪差点弄掉了相机。"
"“你看到了吧，这是真的。告诉我这是真的。”安迪说着疯狂地把更多的胶卷塞进已经磨损的相机里。你和其余的船员都带着敬畏和惊恐叹服于不可思议的天际线。海水从异星雕像和古代坟茔的巨口中倾泻而出。拉莱耶的黑曜石峡谷中闪过诡异的形体，转瞬即逝。看上去一点也不像是人类能造出来的东西。"
"你呼吸之间不由自主地念出了这座城市的名字。船只驶过宽阔海湾，绕过多石的浅滩，即便向来坚定的露比此刻也是呆若木鸡。靠岸后，探险队在黑沙滩上扎营，面前则是高耸的黑曜石尖塔。塔基的巨门看着就很危险，仿佛是沉默的哨兵。第一晚，探险队的成员几乎一言不发。安迪一整晚都在研究一块镶嵌发光字符的黑曜石，而露比则在精心整理工具包。"
"到了早上，你们商量要走哪条路。蒂林哈斯特提供了足够的潜水设备、登山工具，还有充足的补给，足以深入探索两周再返回沙滩。不过，安迪和露比却有了分歧。安迪想沿着海岸线，到海湾开口，西边崩毁的城墙去。向来喜欢居高临下的露比，却想根据天际线绘出城市的全图。她激动地指着内陆深处，一座遥远的，仿佛大教堂一般的建筑。"

msgid "Depending on which character you want to follow, you will either explore the ancient city from west to east, or east to west. You must decide, as a group:"
msgstr "你可以选择从西往东，或者从东往西探索这座古代城市，具体取决于你想跟随哪位角色。你们必须共同决定："

msgid "Follow Andy along the shoreline to the Western Wall."
msgstr "跟着安迪沿着海岸线去西墙。"

msgid "Accompany Ruby through the Obsidian Canyons toward a massive inland structure."
msgstr "陪着露比穿越黑曜石峡谷，前往巨大的内陆建筑。"

msgid ""
"Something about the distant, ruined wall and submerged spires calls to you. After agreeing to accompany Andy westward, he sighs with relief. “I can handle myself, of course, but if we have to go diving, I’d…”  he looks blankly into the distance for a moment. “I don’t want to worry you, but I could swear I saw something human-shaped swimming below. I’ll be glad for the company.” You look past the black water to the edge of the cove, suddenly apprehensive. Something crests the waves for a moment, then disappears. You have the feeling of being watched."
"“Two weeks, then,” says Ruby, hefting a coil of rope over one shoulder. “We’ll meet back here in two weeks. Don’t forget the diving suits. And don’t get yourself killed. I would hate to lose my favorite rival.”"
msgstr ""
"远方崩毁的城墙和沉没的尖塔中有什么在呼唤着你。你同意陪安迪往西，他松了口气：“我自己是能搞定啦，但要是我们得潜水的话，我就……”他朝远方失神了一会儿，“我不想烦你，但我发誓看到了底下有些人形的东西在游。能有你陪我很高兴。”你的视线越过黑水，看向海湾的边缘，突然担心起来。有什么东西涌上波涛，随即又消失了。你感到自己被监视了。"
"“那么，两周。”露比说着将一捆绳索扛上肩头，“我们两周后在这儿见面。别忘了潜水服。也别死了。我可讨厌失去自己最喜欢的对手了。”"

msgid "the expedition headed west."
msgstr "探险队向西进发。"

msgid "Choose an investigator to add the Andy Van Nortwick story asset to their deck. It does not count toward their deck size. This card can be found in the <i>Expedition</i> encounter set."
msgstr "选择一位调查员将安迪·范·诺特维克剧情支援加入自己牌库。这张卡牌不计入其牌库卡牌张数。这张卡牌可以在<i>探险</i>遭遇组中找到。"

msgid "Remove 1 [tablet] token from the chaos bag. Add 1 [cultist] token to the chaos bag for the remainder of the campaign."
msgstr "从混乱袋中移除1个[tablet] 标记。在混乱袋中加入1个[cultist]标记，直到剧本结束。"

msgid ""
"Since you landed, you haven’t been able to take your eyes off of the phantasmagoric skyline. After agreeing to accompany her eastward, you catch the faintest hint of a smile from Ruby. “Fine, you can come along. As long as you don’t hold me back,” she smirks. A fell wind whistles through the perilous canyons, smelling of ancient decay and another, sweeter smell. Storm clouds churn in the distance threateningly.\n"
"“Let’s return here in two weeks,” Andy says, carefully reloading his camera for the dozenth time since you’ve arrived. Before parting ways, the young reporter passes you the obsidian tablet he found last evening, stammering that he isn’t much of a linguist. “I’m not sure what any of it means, but those glyphs are all over the city. Maybe you’ll have better luck with it.”"
msgstr ""
"向东探险：自打登陆以来，你就没法不看那幻影般的天际线。你同意陪露比往东的时候，发现她嘴角闪过一丝微笑。“好吧，你可以来。只要别拖我的后腿。”她笑道。狂风吹过危险的峡谷，带来远古腐坏的气息—但其中还有另一种芬芳。风暴云在远处翻滚，一看就很危险。"
"“两周后回这儿来。”安迪说着小心翼翼地装填相机，自打你们抵达，他已经装了十几次了。分开前，年轻的[[记者]]给了你一块昨晚发现的黑曜石碑匾，支支吾吾地说他可不是个语言学家。“我一点也不确定那是什么意思，但上面的字符全城都是也许在你手里能运气好点。”"

msgid "Choose an investigator to add the Ruby Standish story asset to their deck. It does not count toward their deck size. This card can be found in the <i>Expedition</i> encounter set."
msgstr "选择一位调查员将露比·斯坦德希剧情支援加入自己牌库。这张卡牌不计入其牌库卡牌张数。这张卡牌可以在<i>探险</i>遭遇组中找到."

msgid "the expedition headed east."
msgstr "探险队向东进发。"
